    "Acting as a virtual friend, the system aims to facilitate healthcare couseling to potential patients.",
    "In addition, an increasing number of studies claim that LLMs can benefit mental healthcare systems (Aydın & Karaarslan 2022, Ayers et al. 2023, Kanjee et al. 2023, Sharma et al. 2023, Shryock 2023).",
    "That is because unlike search engines, which provide responses and links when they receive text inputs, chatbots like GPT-4 deliver reponses that are similar to human conversations.",
